Data Deletion Request

Users may request deletion of any associated app data by contacting us at:

📧 mpailden@gmail.com

Since the App stores user data locally on the device, you may also delete your data anytime by:

Clearing the app data in your device settings, or
Uninstalling the App

For subscription-related data (handled by RevenueCat and Google Play), users can manage or cancel subscriptions directly via their Google Play account.
